biotools.summary: ComplexBrowser is a R based software for supervised analysis of changes in protein complex abundance and subunit co-expression in proteomic datasets. It uses information contained in CORUM and EBI Complex Portal databases to provide the user with visualizations helping with biological interpretation of obtained results. ComplexBrowser also incorporates a normalization and quality control steps.
